</entry>
<entry valign="top" align="left">
<list list-type="bulleted" id="list-00031">
<item>Elevated levels: possible inflammation; seen in chronic <term class="no-emphasis" id="term-00133">sinusitis</term> and <term class="no-emphasis" id="term-00134">hypersensitivity reactions.</term></item>
