</list>
</entry>
<entry valign="top" align="left">
<list list-type="bulleted" id="list-00043">
<item>Elevated levels: possible COPD, asthma, pneumonia, anesthesia effects, or use of opioids (respiratory acidosis)</item>
<item>Decreased levels: <term class="no-emphasis" id="term-00155">hyperventilation</term>/<term class="no-emphasis" id="term-00156">respiratory alkalosis</term></item></list></entry>
</row>
