<item>22–26 mEq/L</item></list></entry>
<entry valign="top" align="left">
<list list-type="bulleted" id="list-00047">
<item>Elevated levels: possible respiratory acidosis as compensation for primary <term class="no-emphasis" id="term-00160">metabolic alkalosis</term></item>
<item>Decreased levels: possible respiratory alkalosis as compensation for a primary metabolic acidosis</item>
</list>
</entry>
